{"tid":761055,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[休班+當更警各入一球]警員承認偷拍裙底候判　暫委裁判官稱判服務令不合適","createTime":"2018-07-30T05:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T08:18:34.000Z","uid":51271,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b51f071bc032f2ae114d6972555c565e634f0d46","tid":761055,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:21:16.000Z","msg":"一名27歲警員因偷拍裙底被控一項有違公德行為罪，以及19項不誠實使用電腦罪，案件在西九龍裁判法院提堂。被告承認全部控罪，案件押至下月13日，等待背景報告，被告需還柙候判。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情時指，被告在家庭、經濟、感情及工作方面於案發前出現翻天覆地變化，為被告帶來很大的衝擊，因此有嚴重抑鬱症，未能有效控制於衝動下作出的反社會行為。辯方強調被告與同類案件的犯案人不同，亦非知法犯法的警員，需要面對的是抑鬱症的病情。<br />\n<br />\n暫委裁判官劉淑嫻表示，由於案情嚴重，考慮社會對被告作為的厭惡性，加上被告的行為涉及不同女性，更在當值期間犯案，判以社會服務令並不合適。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告在去年10月在旺角港鐵站以電話偷拍正在乘搭電梯的女子的裙底，以及在油麻地警署當值期間，偷拍一名女同事的裙底。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1409592-20180730.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1409592-20180730.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=GabojfsCkB0Nh5lPrhQ4kuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=3e30ca04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1409592-20180730.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=47abb2b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1409592-20180730.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"dbfec4f2316c281b35fdab71a338688f19f24886","tid":761055,"uid":131157,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:22:37.000Z","msg":"19項控罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d15473ba1f139b7d46fabe9b8667082e11756f","tid":761055,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:29:47.000Z","msg":"局長冇講錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d706d4c74d8d59c7a89fbc674e079d4da6f8234","tid":761055,"uid":82532,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"cit